{"tid":1575753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你班友仔同我入黎，記者唔係condom","createTime":"2019-09-17T03:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T06:33:19.000Z","uid":3013,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"93ebddc1d73e9772323996b62d2cf08ffb03cdbd","tid":1575753,"uid":3013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:12:40.000Z","msg":"借朋友a/c 一用：<br />\n<br />\n屌！警狗出沒！濫捕記者！同我推爆佢！<br />\n<br />\n班仆街黑警自己黑就覺得人人都黑！濫「暴」之後，依家仲濫「捕」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！之前PS、TG直射記者，915就升呢到水炮車射記者，拘捕學生記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（尋晚知衰放咗），但係仲有個網媒記者到依家仲被班冚家剷扣留緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！佢哋明顯想以殺一警百的方式，恐嚇傳媒，滅聲！！進一步控制香港言論自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關連結：<br />\n<br />\n1）<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/620868175077405/posts/657018421462380?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F620868175077405%2Fposts%2F657018421462380%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=3c589371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/620868175077405/posts/657018421462380?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n2）<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/620868175077405/posts/657369844760571?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F620868175077405%2Fposts%2F657369844760571%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=ceba6990\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/620868175077405/posts/657369844760571?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n3）<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/620868175077405/posts/657730891391133?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https:/